title: Mucenieks
text: Mucenieks (<a href="Latvian%20orthography%23Old%20orthography">Old orthography</a>: "Mutzeneek"; feminine: <a href="Muceniece">Muceniece</a>) is a <a href="Latvian%20people">Latvian</a> <a href="occupational%20surname">occupational surname</a>, derived from the <a href="Latvian%20language">Latvian</a> word for "<a href="cooper%20%28profession%29">cooper</a>".
